data.description: Price Reduced!!!! 5 Bedrooms PLUS Bonus Room and Pool in Lake Park! This custom built 3257 sqft home has solar panels which drastically reduces the utility bill! Downstairs is perfect for entertaining with a cozy family room off of the kitchen with a wood burning fireplace and formal dining room. The kitchen features updated cabinets with Silestone countertops, a subway tile backsplash, center island with butcher block countertop, a large breakfast nook, and the stainless steel appliances are included! There is another room , seperate from the others, that would be perfect for a small office, reading room, or formal living room. One guest bedroom with double closets and one full bathroom with single vanity are also located downstairs. The foyer staircase will lead you to the additional bedrooms that are spacious and feature new carpet, double closets and ceiling fans. The guest full bath has a single sink vanity with updated extended countertop and showetub combo. The master bedroom features a bay window that overlooks the relaxing pool, one amble closet and an additional large walk in closet! The unique master bathroom features a shower/tub combo with single vanity and a completey seperate vanity room with an additional sink and sitting area. The upstairs bonus room can be accessed thru the double garage by an additional staircase! Enjoy the fenced backyard grilling on the open patio or lounging by the in ground pool. In addition, the downstairs HVAC was replaced in 2023, the diving board and pool liner were replaced in 2019, the pool pump was replaced in 2023, and there is an active transferable termite bond! Call today to schedule a tour and make this house your home!
